{
  "stem": "3002.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I remember I was in snow till my knees.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But we made it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We came over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that's where I found my brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He made his way by foot from the forest to Ostrog.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Ostrog.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was there with his family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to his house, and my friend went there, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but my friend, after a couple of days, when he looked at-- there were a lot of Russian soldiers around.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was the elegant type.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When he looked at the Russian uniforms, he told me that he's not going to put on one of those.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he made his way back to Przedborz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he-- I heard that he was killed by-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was involved in some monkey business or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stayed with my brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sister went to Lwow because--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's-- you see, my brother and my sister married a brother and a sister from the other family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a criss-cross match.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my-- since they were very rich people in town, in Ostrog, when the Russians came in, the parents of-- the in-laws from the other side, they ran to Lwow because they were afraid of the Russians.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were afraid of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were afraid of the Russians because they were the rich capitalists.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So whom I found in Ostrog is only my brother, his family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sister was already in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Can you spell the name of that place for us?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lwow?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "L-W-O-W.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "O with the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--thing on top.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, that was in '39 I arrived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I stayed till, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] till the Germans came in there, in '41.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that wasn't all.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
